              <span id="reviewTextContainer966545709" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12919383624971397277">I really enjoyed this! This is a book about &apos;wanjala&apos;, the hunger season in Kenya. How can farmers of maize, be net buyers of maize? How can farmers be starving? These are the questions that the One Acre Fund are solving. They provide micro credit, insurance, education, fertilizer and technology (seeds).<br/><br/>Some thoughts here; <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='https://act65com.wordpress.com/2018/03/14/the-last-hunger-season/'>https://act65com.wordpress.com/2018/0...</a>.</span>
  <span id="freeText12919383624971397277" style="display:none">I really enjoyed this! This is a book about 'wanjala', the hunger season in Kenya. How can farmers of maize, be net buyers of maize? How can farmers be starving? These are the questions that the One Acre Fund are solving. They provide micro credit, insurance, education, fertilizer and technology (seeds).<br /><br />Some thoughts here; <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="https://act65com.wordpress.com/2018/03/14/the-last-hunger-season/">https://act65com.wordpress.com/2018/0...</a>.</span>
  <a data-text-id="12919383624971397277" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


